con:testCase.name: HidePayment
con:testCase.con:description:
This testcase displays the flow for Hide action. Here a payment is created and then Hide action is performed on the payment.
Expected Flow: Payment Create -> TBAP -> Action -> Cancel -> Hide Action -> Hidden status -Y-
